info.author: Jason P. Smith
info.description:
A program for counting directed cliques in directed graphs, adapted from https://github.com/luetge/flagser

Official source code repo: https://github.com/JasonPSmith/flagser-count

Requirements: numpy ≥ 1.17.0 and cmake version ≥ 3.9.
info.name: pyflagsercount
info.summary: A package for counting directed cliques in directed graphs
